{"id":177416,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/09/绝版西藏-当琼村/","date":"2011-09-06T05:00:16Z","modified":"2011-09-07T01:07:50Z","title":"绝版西藏-当琼村","content":"<p>当琼村，让人惊艳又安详。</p>\n<p>村子依山而建，背靠大山，面朝圣湖，当穷寺建在村庄之上。</p>\n<p>山、湖、村庄、寺庙的布局，是如此天衣无缝的协调，不可多，也不能少。</p>\n<p>劳作的村民，嬉闹的孩子，虔诚的信徒，如此和谐，仿佛步入天界。</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://img1.blogbuscdn.com/pindao/2011/9/5/63b81aa26b896518c614c1f4d658ce59.jpg\" alt=\"1\" width=\"640\" height=\"426\" /></p>\n<p>1.清晨去放羊的村民</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://img1.blogbuscdn.com/pindao/2011/9/5/e326a5d6adce2e2bc1f830522ea42e78.jpg\" alt=\"2\" width=\"640\" height=\"426\" /></p>\n<p>2.清晨的村子，远处是雪山与圣湖</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://img1.blogbuscdn.com/pindao/2011/9/5/936d9b6da2154213e3808ead715635b9.jpg\" alt=\"3\" width=\"640\" height=\"530\" /></p>\n<p>3.唐卡画师给我们看照片，他为日喀则的寺庙画画，照片里他们在寺庙里的合影</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://img1.blogbuscdn.com/pindao/2011/9/5/547206960c60e7fe4bac1b2153fbcea4.jpg\" alt=\"4\" width=\"640\" height=\"415\" /></p>\n<p>4.母亲与孩子</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://img1.blogbuscdn.com/pindao/2011/9/5/96721817e068947174232f4814871ecf.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"393\" height=\"600\" /></p>\n<p>5.四个女孩</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://img1.blogbuscdn.com/pindao/2011/9/5/d1ac73c035bff0ed9d793e43d80723fe.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"399\" height=\"600\" /></p>\n<p>6.另一个害羞的女孩躲在身后</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://img1.blogbuscdn.com/pindao/2011/9/5/173a35fcee948b3697da56f783bd39f1.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"399\" height=\"600\" /></p>\n<p>7.孩子们，快乐的孩子们</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://img1.blogbuscdn.com/pindao/2011/9/5/e7da2ad2b46d6351d75c7ef03f9543de.jpg\" alt=\"5\" width=\"640\" height=\"426\" /></p>\n<p>8.我们也有虔诚的信仰</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://img1.blogbuscdn.com/pindao/2011/9/5/4856d594357ccfa2f6a1e6dc28fafe21.jpg\" alt=\"6\" width=\"640\" height=\"426\" /></p>\n<p>9.夕阳的背影，映出山的轮廓，安详的当琼措</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://img1.blogbuscdn.com/pindao/2011/9/5/743e5cf49a31cea74e79eedca972f085.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"400\" height=\"600\" /></p>\n<p>10.银河，在夜空中清晰的呈现，如同生命的纹路</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://img1.blogbuscdn.com/pindao/2011/9/5/3c7497def82d6773b5e7fd8de4384028.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"400\" height=\"600\" /></p>\n<p>11.星空下的当琼寺，亮着灯的窗户便是我们的房间，黑夜里最后一张独白。</p>\n<p>Tag:<br />\n<a href=\"http://pindao.blogbus.com/sejie/tag/%E8%A7%86%E7%95%8C\">视界</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://pindao.blogbus.com/sejie/tag/%E7%BA%AA%E5%AE%9E\">纪实</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://pindao.blogbus.com/sejie/tag/%E8%A5%BF%E8%97%8F\">西藏</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://pindao.blogbus.com/sejie/tag/%E5%BD%93%E7%90%BC\">当琼</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://app.home.blogbus.com/share?url=http%3A%2F%2Fcastle1943.blogbus.com%2Flogs%2F159676432.html&amp;c_f=rss\">分享</a>这篇文章，或<a href=\"http://pindao.blogbus.com/sejie/2011090518062.html#cmt_form\">留下</a>你的观点</p>\n<p>我们猜你还喜欢：</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"http://pindao.blogbus.com/sejie/2011090118041.html\">抓住夏天的尾巴</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://pindao.blogbus.com/sejie/2011090118040.html\">醒</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://pindao.blogbus.com/sejie/2011090118037.html\">午后闲话</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://pindao.blogbus.com/sejie/2011083018036.html\">暖</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://pindao.blogbus.com/xingzhe/2011083018034.html\">藏游回忆</a></li>\n</ul>\n<p><a href=\"http://banjiabangzhu.blogbus.com/logs/75886477.html?utm_source=blogbus&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=banjia\">MSN spaces搬家，给您一个更安全、更有保障的方案！</a><img src=\"http://pindao.blogbus.com/sejie/2011090518062.html_.gif\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</p>\n<form action=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/f.fbz?AddNewUserDirect\" method=\"POST\"> 定期获得翻墙信息？<a href=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/?Sub=750556\">请电邮订阅数字时代</a></p></form>\n","author":1,"categories":[20534],"tags":[8643]}